{{monster info}}

==Useful Info==
'''Arcanists''' are spell casters who can blast you and make you [[fragile]]. Fortunately, they are flimsy. They can be found in late [[Dungeon]] and [[Vaults]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Arcanists can deal high damage, but they aren't too [[ev]]asive, cannot [[see invisible]], and don't have much [[willpower]].
*[[Willpower]] helps avoid being [[vitrify|vitrified]], while cold resistance helps defend against [[Bolt of Cold]].
*A [[silence]]d or [[waterlog]]ged arcanist can only do weak melee attacks.

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|arcanists will cast [[Searing Ray]] instead of [[Force Lance]].}}
*In [[0.31]], arcanists were added to the game, split off from [[wizard (monster)|wizards]]. 

[[Category:Human]]
